    "Silvana Armani is the niece of billionaire fashion designer Giorgio Armani (d. September 2025) and the daughter of his late brother Sergio Armani.",
    "She is a board member of Armani's namesake fashion firm and leads the womenswear division. She is also seen as her uncle's stylistic successor.",
    "Under the terms of Armani's will, Silvana is entitled to 17% of the net proceeds from the sale or public listing of 45% of the company within five years of Armani's death.",
    "She also inherited some of Armani's shares in eyewear giant EssilorLuxottica as well as a stake in Armani's superyacht and his empire of luxury homes."
